name: PetMyEasterBunny
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pet my easter bunny
des:
An easter special!

Be the best digital pet owner! Walk, feed, sleep and wash your Easter Bunny to get its health and energy to 100%. Once at 100% your Easter Bunny can do tricks, enjoy belly rubs, fart and burp on command, play with the squeaky toy and play fetch.

Keep coming back to the skill to make sure your Easter Bunny is healthy and it's energy and levels are at 100%.

Disclaimer: These are digital pets, it is just a game. Please do not try doing some of these actions in real life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
